# Seven Fortunas Infrastructure - Code Owners
#
# This file defines code ownership for the Seven Fortunas infrastructure project.
# GitHub will automatically request reviews from the designated owners when pull
# requests modify these files.
#
# Format: path/to/files @owner-username @team-slug
# Documentation: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

