# ============================================================================
# Team Definitions
# ============================================================================
#
# The following teams should be created in the GitHub organization:
#
# @Seven-Fortunas-Internal/devops-team
#   - Primary owners of infrastructure, CI/CD, and automation
#   - Members: DevOps engineers, SREs
#
# @Seven-Fortunas-Internal/security-team
#   - Owners of security, compliance, and audit code
#   - Members: Security engineers, compliance specialists
#
# @Seven-Fortunas-Internal/data-team
#   - Owners of dashboards, metrics, and data aggregation
#   - Members: Data engineers, analytics developers
#
# @Seven-Fortunas-Internal/architecture-team
#   - Owners of architectural decisions and documentation
#   - Members: Architects, senior engineers
#
# @Seven-Fortunas-Internal/product-team
#   - Owners of product requirements and specifications
#   - Members: Product managers, business analysts
#
# @Seven-Fortunas-Internal/qa-team
#   - Owners of testing and validation scripts
#   - Members: QA engineers, test automation specialists
#
# @Seven-Fortunas-Internal/legal-team
#   - Owners of legal documents (LICENSE, etc.)
#   - Members: Legal counsel, compliance officers
#
# ============================================================================
